  <div class="pane-content">
    
<div class="b-title absolute titleCoin mainTitleCoin">
    <h1 class="uppercase ">Médiathèque Guy-L.-Coté</h1>
</div>  </div>

  
  </div>        </div>
        <!--FIN .header-->

        <div class="s-clr wrapper">            

            <div class="main">
                <div id="content" class="m-rr">
                    <div class="panel-pane pane-content-field pane-field-lead" >
  
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="field field-type-text field-field-lead">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <p>The M&eacute;diath&egrave;que Guy-L.-Cot&eacute; holds the Cin&eacute;math&egrave;que&rsquo;s documentation collections.</p>
        </div>
        </div>
</div>
  </div>

  
  </div><div class="panel-region-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-node-body" >
  
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <p><img alt="" src="/sites/default/files/files/pages/images/mediatheque.png" style="width: 131px; height: 163px; float: right;" />It enables users to access these vast archival holdings with the help of experienced documentalists who are available to assist them with their research. Various databases, including that of the International Federation of Film Archives (FIAF), can be consulted onsite.<br />
	&nbsp;<br />
	Although archives may only be consulted onsite, photocopiers and printers are available for users.</p>
<p>	The M&eacute;diath&egrave;que Guy-L.-Cot&eacute; is an invaluable resource for anyone with an interest in our audiovisual heritage &ndash; past, present and future!<br />
	&nbsp;</p>
<h3>
	Rates</h3>
<p>Admission to the M&eacute;diath&egrave;que is free to all. There is a charge for photographic reproductions and photocopies.</p>
<h3>
	Specialized services</h3>
<p>Research and digitization services are available to individuals and businesses for a fee.</p>
<h3>
	Recent acquisitions</h3>
<p>See our recent acquisitions in the&nbsp;<a href="http://collections.cinematheque.qc.ca/mediatheque/nouveautes/2016/">Collections</a>.</p>
<h3>
	Opening Hours</h3>
<p>Monday to Friday: 9:30 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.<br />
	<span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps">Access to</span> <span class="hps">new documents</span> <span class="hps">can not</span> <span class="hps">be done in</span> <span class="hps">30 minutes</span> <span class="hps">before closing.</span></span></p>
<h3>
	Contact</h3>
<p><a href="mailto:mediatheque@cinematheque.qc.ca">mediatheque@cinematheque.qc.ca</a><br />
	&nbsp;</p>
  </div>

  
